These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: drama, sports, romance, epic, musical, mystery, zombie
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: techno, hip-hop, house, indie, country, folk, ambient
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, badminton, soccer, sailing, cycling, rowing
 1. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of techno##2
 4. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 6. the person watching drama movies is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 7. the fan of indie is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person watching musical movies##2
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 9. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
10. the person watching zombie movies is the fan of house##1
11. the fan of folk is the person watching epic movies##1
12. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
13. the person who's sport is baseball is the fan of country##1
14. the person watching mystery movies is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | drama     | mystery | sports | epic | zombie  | romance  |
| Music-Genre   | techno  | indie        | hip-hop  | ambient     | folk   | house       | country   |
| Sport         | ice-hockey   | rowing | soccer    | badminton  | sailing | cycling | baseball |

