.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: spanish, malaysian, mexican, indonesian, dutch, nigerian, australian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: water-polo, tennis, climbing, cycling, golf, ice-hockey, rugby
The people use 7 different means of transport: tram, bike, taxi, airplane, snowmobile, boat, jet-ski
 1. the malaysian is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 2. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's sport is golf##1
 3. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is the australian##1
 6. the spanish is the person driving the airplane##1
 7. the spanish is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person driving the jet-ski##2
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the dutch##1
 9. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
10. the mexican is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
11. the dutch is on the right of the spanish##1
12. the person driving the tram is the malaysian##1
13. the indonesian is on the left of the spanish##1
14. the indonesian is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
15. the malaysian is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | nigerian | australian      | indonesian     | spanish  | dutch | mexican | malaysian |
| Sport         | tennis  | water-polo | ice-hockey | climbing | rugby | cycling   | golf  |
| Transport     | taxi   | boat     | jet-ski        | airplane  | snowmobile   | bike       | tram      |

