.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, almond-milk, sprite, juice, cola, mirinda
The people have 7 different jobs:  videographer, nurse, electrician, firefighter, dancer, librarian, mechanic
The people use 7 different means of transport: car, subway, jet-ski, skateboard, quad-bike, airplane, tram
 1. the person driving the subway is the videographer##1
 2. the person driving the quad-bike is the firefighter##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the dancer##1
 4. the person driving the jet-ski is the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the person driving the airplane is between the person driving the tram and the mechanic##2
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 7. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the mechanic##1
 9. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
10. the electrician is on the right of the librarian##1
11. the person driving the subway is the videographer##1
12. the electrician is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the firefighter##1
14. the person driving the tram is the person drinking mirinda##1
15. the person driving the car is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate     | juice   | cola        | 7up   | almond-milk     | sprite     | mirinda    |
