.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-4::.
There 7 different types of food: pepper, artichoke, pineapple, tomato, watermelon, lime, spinach
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: disaster, superhero, martial-arts, epic, western, fantasy, horror
There are 7 different nationalities: german, indonesian, chinese, argentine, brazilian, japanese, british
 1. the brazilian is on the far left##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is the person eating tomato##1
 3. the chinese is the person watching epic movies##1
 4. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
 5. the german is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 6. the person eating pineapple is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating pepper is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 9. the japanese is the person watching disaster movies##1
10. the german is the person eating watermelon##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is the british##1
12. the person eating artichoke is the brazilian##1
13. the argentine is on the far right##1
14. the person watching horror movies is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person watching epic movies##2
15. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |    4    |     5      |     6      |     7     |
| Food          | artichoke  | lime    | watermelon  | pepper | tomato  | spinach | pineapple |
| Movie-Genre   | western | martial-arts | horror   | epic   | fantasy | disaster     | superhero |
