.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-16::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  engineer, chef, mechanic, videographer, accountant, librarian, architect
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: country, funk, disco, indie, pop, r&b, soul
7 different pets are kept: rat, goldfish, dog, cat, goat, turtle, rabbit
 1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the mechanic##1
 2. the owner of the turtle is between the fan of pop and the fan of disco##2
