 4. the fan of soul is on the left of the librarian##1
 5. the fan of country is the engineer##1
 6. the mechanic is in the middle##1
 7. the accountant is the fan of r&b##1
 8. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the fan of country is the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the architect is the owner of the goat##1
