.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-20::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, mirinda, water, tea, juice, lemonade
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, cooking, reading, rock-climbing, chess, drawing, baking
7 different pets are kept: pony, hamster, hedgehog, goat, rabbit, rat, dog
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 2. the owner of the rat is in the middle##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the rat is the person drinking water##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 8. the owner of the goat is between the person who's hobby is reading and the owner of the hedgehog##2
 9. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
11. the person drinking tea is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
13. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
14. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the owner of the dog and the person who's hobby is baking##2
15. the owner of the dog is the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5      |      6      |     7     |
